305
00:30:37,080 --> 00:30:38,490
Sepertinya dia mempertanyakannya..

306
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:43,080
Dia bertanya,"Halo? Siapa kamu?".

307
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:46,960
Kalau begitu Kiriyama,
