308
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:56,060
<i>Aku...</i>

309
00:30:56,060 --> 00:30:57,390
<i>...Rei Kiriyama.</i>

310
00:30:58,060 --> 00:31:02,050
<i>Grup kedua kelas B, Roku-dan, 18 tahun.</i>

311
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:06,520
<i>Aku belajar shogi dari ayahku.</i>

312
00:31:07,150 --> 00:31:10,390
<i>Tapi ketika aku berada di kelas 3 sekolah dasar...</i>

313
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:18,570
